title: 215. Andy, DJ & Tommy Vext CTI: Hillary Clinton 2024?, Nike Firing Employees? & The Future Of Fitness?
itunes:title: 215. Andy, DJ & Tommy Vext CTI: Hillary Clinton 2024?, Nike Firing Employees? & The Future Of Fitness?
description: In today's episode, Andy, DJ & Tommy discuss Democrats rallying behind Hillary Clinton for the 2024 presidential race, Nike preparing to fire all unvaccinated employees on January 15th and the article in Self magazine promoting obesity as a healthy future of fitness.
